# ET AI Concierge: Financial Life Navigator

### Project Overview
[cite_start]A multi-agent system that understands a user's financial life in one conversation to guide them through the ET ecosystem[cite: 93].

### Core Agentic Framework
- [cite_start]**Profiler**: A chat agent that greets users and maps them to ET products.
- [cite_start]**Life Navigator**: Understands the user's complete financial life to identify portfolio gaps[cite: 96, 98].
- [cite_start]**Marketplace Agent**: Connects users to financial services through ET partnerships.

### Technical Features
- [cite_start]**Workflow Automation**: Full task completion with built-in exception handling[cite: 16, 24].
- [cite_start]**Audit Trails**: Maintains auditable reasoning at each step for compliance[cite: 64, 71].
